the peach tree ( hangul : 복숭아나무 ; rr : boksunga namu ) is a 2012 south korean film directed by actress ku hye-sun . it stars jo seung-woo and ryu deok-hwan as conjoined twin brothers who fall in love with the same woman played by nam sang-mi . the film premiered at the 2011 busan international film festival , and was released in theaters a year later . in 2013 it was also invited to the brussels international fantastic film festival , taiwan 's golden horse fantastic film festival , and the new york asian film festival .